profile_positions.description:
- Responsible to effectively support new partners (vacation homes, single hotels, inns) to become available on the platform and to support existing partners to increase business value, by outbound calling and email.  
- Demonstration of the platform to the new partners, competitive advantages, commercial conditions and strategies, negotiation of possible objections, for a better performance on the website; 
- Delivery of trainings by phone to guarantee the conditions of the property are in accordance with the platform’s requirements; 
- Availability and implementation of products based on partner’s needs;
- Participation in a project focused on upselling, presenting a portfolio of several Booking.com products and its advantages with the focus to convert partners;
- Achievement of targets on a quarterly basis closely monitored by the New Partner Services area
